article_title: 10 things you may not have known about the Senate candidates

og.description: Sen. Mark Warner, D-Va., and Republican opponent Ed Gillespie will address the Virginia Municipal League conference meeting in Roanoke today, and then will appear at a candidates’ forum with Libertarian candidate Robert Sarvis at Charter Hall in the Roanoke City Market Building.
